    "Name": "Padilla (LRM)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Padilla Heavy Artillery Tank (LRM)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>5/8 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>375 XL</color></b>\n\nThe Padilla Heavy Artillery Tank, a Star League-era vehicle, was designed for long-range missile fire alongside the Chaparral. Although most were destroyed during the Amaris Civil War, a few survived into the 31st century, serving with ComStar's Com Guards and the Second Star League's SLDF.\n\nThis variant results from House Liao's inability to produce more Arrow IV missiles during the First Succession War. Their surviving vehicles were refitted with a pair of LRM-20s with two tons of ammunition.",
